  I've completed the comprehensive UI overhaul implementation. Here's what was created:

  Foundation (Phase 0)

  - tailwind.config.js - Tailwind configuration with semantic color tokens, Inter font, custom colors
  - static/css/input.css - Tailwind source with CSS variables for light/dark themes, truncation utilities
  - package.json - Updated with Tailwind dependencies and build scripts
  - ./dev - Added css, css-build, css-prod commands

  Primitives (Phases 1-3)

  - ui/primitives/text.py - Typography: PageTitle, SectionTitle, CardTitle, Subtitle, BodyText, SmallText, Caption, TruncatedText
  - ui/primitives/layout.py - Layout with overflow fixes: Container, Stack, Row, FlexItem (with min-w-0!), Grid
  - ui/primitives/card.py - Cards: Card, CardLink, CardHeader, CardBody, CardFooter
  - ui/primitives/badge.py - Badges: Badge, StatusBadge, PriorityBadge
  - ui/primitives/button.py - Buttons: Button, ButtonLink, IconButton
  - ui/primitives/input.py - Forms: Input, Textarea, SelectInput, Checkbox

  Patterns (Phase 4)

  - ui/patterns/entity_card.py - EntityCard for all 14 domains with proper truncation
  - ui/patterns/stats_grid.py - StatCard, StatsGrid for dashboard metrics
  - ui/patterns/empty_state.py - EmptyState for empty lists

  Layouts (Phase 5)

  - ui/layouts/page.py - PageHead, PageLayout, SimplePageLayout
  - ui/layouts/dashboard.py - DashboardLayout, DashboardSection

  POC: Docs Components (Phase 6)

  - ui/docs/components.py - New docs components: SectionCard, SectionGrid, TopicList, HomeHero, Breadcrumbs
  - ui/docs/layout.py - New DocsLayout and create_docs_page using raw Tailwind



